<p>Companies in growth mode should lean toward the higher end. Established companies with strong existing rankings can spend less to maintain and slowly expand.</p>
<h3>Factor 2: Your Industry Competition</h3>
<p>A local plumber in a small city needs a different budget than a SaaS company targeting "project management software." The more competitive your target keywords, the higher your required investment in content depth and link building.</p>
