<h2>Quarter-by-Quarter Budget Phasing</h2>
<p>SEO budgets should not stay static. Phase your spending to match where you are in the SEO growth cycle.</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" alt="Quarter-by-quarter SEO budget phasing timeline" src="/images/blog/seo-budget-quarterly-phasing.webp" /></p>
<h3>Q1: Foundation (Months 1-3)</h3>
<p><strong>Focus:</strong> Technical fixes + content foundation + strategy.</p>
<div class="table-wrap"><table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Category</th>
<th>Q1 Allocation</th>
